<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Interview Scheduled - COMSATS Internship Portal</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Reset styles */
        body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        table, td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }
        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            border: 0;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            background-color: #f8fafc !important;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif !important;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ea580c 0%, #f97316 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            width: 200px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            color: #ea580c;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .logo-subtitle {
            color: #f97316;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #fed7aa;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .interview-icon {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .interview-circle {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ea580c 0%, #f97316 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.3);
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .interview-details {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed 0%, #ffedd5 100%);
            border: 2px solid #f97316;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .interview-details h3 {
            color: #ea580c;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 12px 0;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            color: #9a3412;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            min-width: 100px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #7c2d12;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .urgent-notice {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .urgent-notice h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .urgent-notice p {
            color: #b91c1c;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .preparation-tips {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .preparation-tips h3 {
            color: #0369a1;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .preparation-tips ul {
            color: #0369a1;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .preparation-tips li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ea580c 0%, #f97316 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.3);
        }
        
        .secondary-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #374151 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-text">COMSATS</div>
                <div class="logo-subtitle">UNIVERSITY</div>
            </div>
            <h1>Interview Scheduled!</h1>
            <p>Your Interview Has Been Confirmed</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            
            <div class="greeting">
                Interview Invitation for {{studentName}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Congratulations! <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has reviewed your application and would like to invite you 
                for an interview for the <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> position. This is an exciting opportunity to showcase your skills and learn more about the role.
            </div>
            
            <!-- Interview Details -->
            <div class="interview-details">
                <h3>üìÖ Interview Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Date:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewDate}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Time:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewTime}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Duration:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewDuration}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Type:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewType}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if interviewLocation}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Location:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewLocation}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if meetingLink}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Meeting Link:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><a href="{{meetingLink}}" style="color: #ea580c;">{{meetingLink}}</a></div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Interviewer:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewerName}} ({{interviewerTitle}})</div>
                </div>
                {{#if interviewerEmail}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Contact:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{interviewerEmail}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <!-- Urgent Notice -->
            <div class="urgent-notice">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notice</h3>
                <p><strong>Please confirm your attendance within 24 hours</strong></p>
                <p>If you cannot attend, contact the company immediately to reschedule</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Preparation Tips -->
            <div class="preparation-tips">
                <h3>üéØ Interview Preparation Tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Research the Company:</strong> Study {{companyName}}'s background, values, and recent projects</li>
                    <li><strong>Review Job Description:</strong> Understand the {{jobTitle}} role requirements thoroughly</li>
                    <li><strong>Prepare Questions:</strong> Have thoughtful questions about the role and company culture</li>
                    <li><strong>Technical Preparation:</strong> Review relevant technical skills and concepts</li>
                    <li><strong>Documents Ready:</strong> Have your resume, portfolio, and academic transcripts available</li>
                    <li><strong>Professional Attire:</strong> Dress appropriately for the interview format</li>
                    <li><strong>Test Technology:</strong> If online, test your camera, microphone, and internet connection</li>
                    <li><strong>Arrive Early:</strong> Plan to arrive 10-15 minutes before the scheduled time</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{confirmAttendanceUrl}}" class="cta-button">Confirm Attendance</a>
                <a href="{{companyProfileUrl}}" class="secondary-button">View Company Profile</a>
            </div>
            
            <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
            
            <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
                <strong>Interview Information:</strong><br>
                ‚Ä¢ Interview ID: {{interviewId}}<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Position: {{jobTitle}} at {{companyName}}<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Application ID: {{applicationId}}<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Scheduled: {{scheduleDate}}<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Reminder: We'll send you a reminder 24 hours before the interview
            </div>
            
            <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                Best of luck with your interview!<br>
                <strong>COMSATS Internship Portal Team</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>COMSATS Internship Portal</strong></p>
            <p>This is an automated notification. For interview inquiries, contact the company directly.</p>
            <p>For technical issues, contact the internship coordinator.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                ¬© 2025 COMSATS University. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>